 ----------------------- USING MAKEFILE -------------------------
 sample commands:

 	# compile the codes
	make

 	# run sample input for 2 iterations
 	make run

 	# run random 2000*2000 board as input for 100 iterations
 	make run-large

 ------------------------- USING SHELL ----------------------------
 sample commands:

 	# run sample input for 2 iterations
 	./main 0 0 2

 	# run random 2000*2000 board as input for 100 iterations
 	./main 2000 2000 100

 ------------------------- OTHERS ----------------------------

 	For printing out the procedure for running game, please set the DEBUG to 1 in the debug_config.h file and compile again.
 
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
